        <mxCell id="env_desc_list" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;scissor_pick_and_place&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Robô: SO-ARM 101 · GR00T N1.5&lt;br&gt;Tarefa: pegar tesoura e colocar na bandeja&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;locomanip_tray_pick_and_place&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Robô: Unitree G1 · GR00T N1.6&lt;br&gt;Tarefa: retirar caixa da prateleira, girar 180°,&lt;br&gt;colocar no carrinho e voltar à postura inicial&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;locomanip_push_cart&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Robô: Unitree G1 · GR00T N1.6&lt;br&gt;Tarefa: ir ao carrinho, segurar alças e empurrar&lt;br&gt;até o destino&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;ultrasound_liver_scan&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Robô: Franka + sonda · openpi PI0&lt;br&gt;Tarefa: ultrassom do fígado em fantoma abdominal&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;assemble_trocar&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Robô: G1 + mãos dex · GR00T N1.5&lt;br&gt;Tarefa: montar trocarte a partir da caixa&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#b85450&quot;&gt;⚠ inference-only (sem fine-tune agentic)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;" parent="1" vertex="1">
